Name: Earth Chain: Earth False/True VI
Desc:
This is a chain skill that shares its skill level with Earth Chain: Earth. Charges rapidly by riding the energy of the earth.
Earth Chain: False does not cause you to take damage even when attacking enemies in the Damage Reflection Status.
Required Skill: Earth Chain: Earth Lv. 20 or higher
